{"tid":741080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉亞仁爆現身「上海Gay Bar」！精壯男友人陪狂歡","createTime":"2018-07-13T11:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T05:52:23.000Z","uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d8d62be404d8d66207f980c62c41ddce29181fa","tid":741080,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1212103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1212103&d=oC%2F2cbnt5wiLF736FStNPNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7d6a7ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1212103</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3413/d3413796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3413%2Fd3413796.jpg&h=94c6e6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲劉亞仁被爆現身上海同志酒吧。（圖／翻攝劉亞仁IG）<br />\n<br />\n記者楊蕎綺／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓「青龍獎影帝」劉亞仁有著變色龍演技，出道以來作品類型多樣化，不過感情世界似不如事業豐富，最近期的一任緋聞女友宋慧喬已結婚，他還擔任致詞人，證明兩人確實只是好友關係，近日他被爆現身上海某Gay Bar，身邊還有幾位精壯鬍渣男陪伴，讓他性向再受到關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3413/d3413786.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3413%2Fd3413786.jpg&h=83bdf29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲有網友直指左一男子就是劉亞仁男友。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3413/d3413795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3413%2Fd3413795.jpg&h=1a49e13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲劉亞仁一度和宋慧喬傳出緋聞，但在對方和宋仲基結婚後，傳言不攻而破。（圖／翻攝<br />\n劉亞仁IG）<br />\n<br />\n劉亞仁出道15年來鮮少傳出緋聞，日前因私人行程現身上海，有幸運粉絲陸續在當地巧遇他、興奮地PO網分享，甚至有網友爆料，親眼目睹他和3名鬍渣男，一起在上海的同志酒吧狂歡，而其中一位精壯男子，更疑似是他的「男友」，不過劉亞仁對爆料目前並無任何回應，影迷對於他的性向爆料似乎也不感驚訝，只紛紛留言：「不管喜歡男的還是女的，支持的是他的演技。」"},{"pid":"68f9a3509b83f51393581bbd553b42b54932f0a5","tid":741080,"uid":169468,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"邊位?"},{"pid":"e7aaecf6a43bd8e1979981206cfd6e3be3e97d91","tid":741080,"uid":1977,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"以為劉松仁先入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c011806f78d09f0929ade443faff061903aefd32","tid":741080,"uid":43816,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"有咩特別？ 又唔係劉松仁被爆現身上海同志酒吧"},{"pid":"b60ceaf939213c548ccd8e0abc5ca6d9390a68a7","tid":741080,"uid":65774,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e7aaecf6a43bd8e1979981206cfd6e3be3e97d91","tid":741080,"uid":1977,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"以為劉松仁先入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/185011_cc6f52848e09a73e44ccf9e70e4f3679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F185011_cc6f52848e09a73e44ccf9e70e4f3679.jpg&h=637374d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eafce97a4c3471eb197310fe9f375eca84ff2411","tid":741080,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"佢都幾有性格"},{"pid":"6252af68653233fe8063d1be89d1b2c878b35c6a","tid":741080,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:48:47.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070b519dadfd4f2e67329c8deddb1c003acf17a8","tid":741080,"uid":147770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/195259_a859b78f4962a8ba31397682731e3ebf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F195259_a859b78f4962a8ba31397682731e3ebf.png&h=b22c3f6b&s=